root: ^I am dyin-g, I ca-n see my dogs in the light..
^Oh no, you’re not going to get out of it that easily.
^You have always been jealous of me, haven’t you?
^Look at you all alone, drunk as a skunk in the early morning.
^You will never find love, not even god will take mercy on your soul.
^The only one not running away is the child trapped inside of you.
^My doctor assured me I was sterile!
^I do admire getting around, but I assume it will make the search for the father… difficult.
